[log] bash[68] stdout unpacked = unpack_upx("malware.exe")
[log] bash[68] stdout if unpacked:
[log] bash[68] stdout     unpacked_size = os.path.getsize("malware.exe")
[log] bash[68] stdout     print(f"Unpacking successful: {original_size} -> {unpacked_size} bytes")
[log] bash[68] stdout else:
[log] bash[68] stdout     print("File is not compressed or unpacking failed")
[log] bash[68] stdout ```
